This paper discusses the innovations and enhancements made to Apache Hive, an open-source relational database system for big data analytics. The paper covers topics such as transactions, optimizer, runtime, and federation, which are all related to database systems and data management. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
